import React from "react";
import CustomButton from "../../../components/button";
import { Card, CardContent, TextField, Typography } from "@mui/material";
import "./index.scss";

function LoginPage() {
  return (
    <Card className="login-card" elevation={0}>
      <CardContent>
        <Typography variant="h5" component="h2" gutterBottom>
          Login
        </Typography>
        <form>
          <TextField
            label="Username"
            variant="outlined"
            fullWidth
            margin="normal"
            className="login-text-field" // Gunakan kelas gaya yang baru saja dibuat
          />
          <TextField
            label="Password"
            type="password"
            variant="outlined"
            fullWidth
            size="medium"
            margin="normal"
            className="login-text-field" // Gunakan kelas gaya yang baru saja dibuat
          />
          <CustomButton fullWidth paddingProp={"21px"}>
            Masuk
          </CustomButton>
        </form>
      </CardContent>
    </Card>
  );
}

export default LoginPage;
